This is a dev texture styled map, inspirated by awpdev from the little maper cRuZeeR. The Texture is by Chris528.

The map is made for my AWP NoScope Server but I'll release this to Gamebanana.

You're probably wondering why this is v6, simply because I'm working on the map for a long time and finally have a stable (not final) version, but still in development.

AWP NoScope Server: 62.75.215.21:27015

Feedback is desired. Have Fun!
